Package: hvtiRhazard
Title: Native R Port of HAZARD Modeling Components
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("John", "Ehrlinger", email = "john.ehrlinger@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides native R implementations of core HAZARD model
    components with a focus on behavioral parity, transparent numerics,
    and reproducible validation against reference outputs. The package
    is intentionally implemented in pure R first; performance-critical
    paths may later be accelerated with Rcpp without changing the public
    interface.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
